{"tid":2405265,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警證供與片出入大  企圖襲警案 20歲仔脫罪","createTime":"2021-02-12T08:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T08:32:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4a2256b494b4ac3541a2389fa82e982609531673","tid":2405265,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T08:23:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210212/GSSKXSJGSZFBHID7VXIYXZT2TA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210212%2FGSSKXSJGSZFBHID7VXIYXZT2TA%2F&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FMrrJHX4TENqAnNRziDaZDA%3D&h=744a4b45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210212%2FGSSKXSJGSZFBHID7VXIYXZT2TA%2F&h=26c973a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210212/GSSKXSJGSZFBHID7VXIYXZT2TA/</a><br />\n<br />\n警證供與片出入大 <br />\n企圖襲警案 20歲仔脫罪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yEos-WnmaecUEV0g-MIArcySQpM=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LMBECXDXENBANGBAEKAY3QSLRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyEos-WnmaecUEV0g-MIArcySQpM%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLMBECXDXENBANGBAEKAY3QSLRY.jpg&h=2f057f68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警員何天佑的證供與新聞片差異大，裁判官表示未能安心倚賴其供詞。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】前年10月27日市民在尖沙嘴遊行追究警暴，傍晚時分警方與市民爆發衝突。一名青年其後被指在九龍城向警員揮舞35厘米長的鐵筆，及後遭搜出一把鉗，被控企圖襲警及管有非法用途工具兩罪。案件昨裁決，裁判官張天雁指現場新聞片段與警員供詞有太大出入，影片未見有人揮動武器，認為不能安心倚賴警員供詞，亦未能確定青年藏有鉗是有非法用途，裁定兩罪罪脫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藏鉗作非法用途不成立<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。，被告右手手持鐵筆，上下揮動約三至四次。惟她反覆觀看現場新聞片段，看不到警員所謂被告揮動鐵筆的動作，亦看不到有人使用或揮動武器。由於何證供與片段內容有太大出入，她不能安心倚賴警員的供詞。<br />\n<br />\n張官又指，警方在三份警誡供詞中，均沒就被告現時被控的罪名警誡被告，即不能肯定從被告背囊內找到的鉗必然有非法用途，裁定被告脫罪。<br />\n<br />\n辯方稱，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC651/20"},{"pid":"4905003bbbb71aa7de79f4853ab3f03b9061e3b1","tid":2405265,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T08:26:29.000Z","msg":"被告袋中有xx，唯一合理可能嘅推論就係要用xx做違法行為<br />\n<br />\n有罪定冇罪，真係靠彩數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22c1eec468a7ed0ca4435ad1345daa29ef41541","tid":2405265,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T08:28:45.000Z","msg":"同十二碼一樣，兩個結果，一係入，一係唔入"},{"pid":"56ade5233775a6157bc549c2bbeeaddb8bc63e1a","tid":2405265,"uid":66234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4905003bbbb71aa7de79f4853ab3f03b9061e3b1","tid":2405265,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T08:26:29.000Z","msg":"被告袋中有xx，唯一合理可能嘅推論就係要用xx做違法行為<br />\n<br />\n有罪定冇罪，真係靠彩數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T08:31:08.000Z","msg":"後生既就用有罪推論"},{"pid":"2196e5ee4dbb72b5da2079bde014ce49deede1b0","tid":2405265,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T08:32:00.000Z","msg":"DOJ: 研究是否上訴"}]}